684
00:52:24,878 --> 00:52:26,548
He's making his move.

685
00:52:26,778 --> 00:52:28,387
We don't have much time.

686
00:52:29,517 --> 00:52:33,387
We'll catch the Imoogi
in Ji A's body today.

687
00:52:37,128 --> 00:52:39,557
Everything must go
exactly as planned.

688
00:52:39,557 --> 00:52:41,427
We get it, so say it.

689
00:52:42,628 --> 00:52:43,927
It's simple.

690
00:52:44,168 --> 00:52:45,898
Ji A will draw her blood...

691
00:52:45,997 --> 00:52:47,367
and lure Imoogi out.

692
00:52:48,208 --> 00:52:51,378
Once he comes out, I'll stab
him with the Sin Slayer.

693
00:52:52,338 --> 00:52:55,048
Shin Ju. Once Ji A and I go in,

694
00:52:55,048 --> 00:52:56,347
lock the door from the outside.

695
00:52:56,977 --> 00:53:00,278
No one can come near us
until I give the signal.

696
00:53:02,847 --> 00:53:03,947
Why not?

697
00:53:03,947 --> 00:53:06,188
By chance if he
escapes from Ji A,

698
00:53:08,088 --> 00:53:09,387
you guys will be in danger.

699
00:53:10,528 --> 00:53:12,227
He may enter one of your bodies.

700
00:53:12,597 --> 00:53:14,867
That's why I made a
border with horse blood.

701
00:53:14,968 --> 00:53:17,668
He's different from the
Imoogi we've known until now.

702
00:53:18,537 --> 00:53:21,338
We don't know what he looks
like or how and where he'd move.

703
00:53:21,838 --> 00:53:23,537
We don't know
anything right now.

704
00:53:23,968 --> 00:53:25,977
We cannot make a single mistake.

705
00:53:25,977 --> 00:53:28,878
What if he goes into you?

706
00:53:30,177 --> 00:53:32,247
That won't happen as
long as I'm conscious.

707
00:53:34,488 --> 00:53:35,588
Shin Ju.

708
00:53:37,387 --> 00:53:41,028
It's a snake. I got one that
is a perfect fit for him.

709
00:53:43,057 --> 00:53:47,157
So, the best is if you
can slay it in one go.

710
00:53:47,157 --> 00:53:48,767
Even if he gets away,

711
00:53:49,628 --> 00:53:52,137
that snake is the only
body he can go into.

712
00:53:54,407 --> 00:53:57,878
Let's go. I want to get rid
of it as soon as possible.

713
00:54:46,188 --> 00:54:47,258
Here's the dagger.

714
00:54:51,927 --> 00:54:54,157
Thank you. You should go.

715
00:54:54,827 --> 00:54:57,798
Please be careful.

716
00:55:41,677 --> 00:55:42,807
Okay, then.

717
00:55:44,208 --> 00:55:45,648
Shall we begin?

718
00:55:46,148 --> 00:55:47,278
But first,

719
00:55:48,617 --> 00:55:51,418
tie me to the chair with this.

720
00:55:52,818 --> 00:55:55,028
What if I hurt you again?

721
00:55:55,227 --> 00:55:56,557
That's unncessary.

722
00:55:56,887 --> 00:55:59,497
Do as I say. Okay?

723
00:56:05,537 --> 00:56:07,568
Why do you keep
trying to protect me?

724
00:56:23,318 --> 00:56:25,287
I have a bad feeling about this.

725
00:56:25,858 --> 00:56:27,617
Don't say that. You'll jinx it.

726
00:56:47,747 --> 00:56:50,247
Okay, then. I'll tie you up.

727
00:56:51,577 --> 00:56:54,177
Okay. Yeon.

728
00:56:56,088 --> 00:56:57,718
Will you give me a hug?

729
00:57:07,155 --> 00:57:10,094
Don't hesitate
because of me, okay?

730
00:57:11,135 --> 00:57:12,365
There's nothing to
be nervous about.

731
00:57:13,034 --> 00:57:14,804
It's only a blunt wooden dagger.

732
00:57:15,235 --> 00:57:17,874
I'm prepared for any
unwanted injuries.

733
00:57:18,374 --> 00:57:19,835
As if I'd let you get hurt.

734
00:57:20,275 --> 00:57:22,905
Besides, this dagger can
only slay the unslayable,

735
00:57:22,905 --> 00:57:24,874
like Imoogi's soul.

736
00:57:26,644 --> 00:57:29,844
Does that mean, it
can also slay...

737
00:57:30,485 --> 00:57:31,514
your soul too?

738
00:57:40,985 --> 00:57:43,826
Don't hesitate
because of me, okay?

739
00:57:44,865 --> 00:57:46,326
There's nothing to
be nervous about.

740
00:57:46,695 --> 00:57:48,496
It's only a blunt wooden dagger.

741
00:57:48,896 --> 00:57:51,536
I'm prepared for any
unwanted injuries.

742
00:57:52,036 --> 00:57:53,505
As if I'd let you get hurt.

743
00:57:53,936 --> 00:57:56,576
Besides, this dagger can
only slay the unslayable,

744
00:57:56,576 --> 00:57:58,606
like Imoogi's soul.

745
00:58:00,345 --> 00:58:03,416
Does that mean, it
can also slay...

746
00:58:04,146 --> 00:58:05,246
your soul too?

747
00:58:07,215 --> 00:58:09,186
Of course, it can.

748
00:58:18,766 --> 00:58:21,465
- But...
- Yes?

749
00:58:23,465 --> 00:58:24,865
I've been meaning to ask.

750
00:58:27,436 --> 00:58:28,436
Who are you?

751
00:58:31,246 --> 00:58:32,345
What's dying...

752
00:58:33,146 --> 00:58:34,275
is your soul.

753
00:58:44,975 --> 00:58:46,176
- You can't.
- Move.

754
00:58:46,336 --> 00:58:48,906
I'll kill her if
anything happens to Yeon.

755
00:58:48,946 --> 00:58:51,745
Do so, but only
over my dead body.

756
00:58:52,575 --> 00:58:53,915
You think that can stop me?

757
00:59:01,685 --> 00:59:02,825
How pathetic.

758
00:59:04,856 --> 00:59:07,595
Who knew you'd actually come in
possession of the Sin Slayer?

759
00:59:12,136 --> 00:59:14,466
Hey. Are you pretending
to be asleep?

760
00:59:26,776 --> 00:59:27,776
Wait.

761
00:59:29,115 --> 00:59:30,716
Did that really kill his soul?

762
01:00:28,676 --> 01:00:30,645
This was inevitable anyway.

763
01:00:38,285 --> 01:00:41,825
So how about it? An
old home for a new one.

764
01:00:54,566 --> 01:00:56,305
Don't you know how pricey
houses are these days?

765
01:00:56,305 --> 01:00:58,035
You little thief.

766
01:00:58,276 --> 01:00:59,935
- What on earth?
- Isn't it obvious?

767
01:01:01,236 --> 01:01:02,645
This is what I
needed to confirm.

768
01:01:04,676 --> 01:01:07,276
So this is how you
jump from body to body.

769
01:01:11,586 --> 01:01:14,316
The fortune teller has been
untraceable since the folk village.

