01:01:14,685 --> 01:01:17,926
Even the Gatekeeper of Samdo River
hasn't been able to spot him.

771
01:01:18,595 --> 01:01:19,825
Darn it.

772
01:01:20,495 --> 01:01:21,526
What now?

773
01:01:22,466 --> 01:01:26,035
Go out and find me a
random wooden dagger.

774
01:01:26,236 --> 01:01:27,296
A wooden dagger?

775
01:01:27,636 --> 01:01:29,836
What use do you have
for a blunt dagger?

776
01:01:30,606 --> 01:01:32,535
To slay the unslayable.

777
01:01:39,946 --> 01:01:42,716
How about we change
the game a bit?

778
01:01:49,285 --> 01:01:50,356
Stop the car.

779
01:01:58,236 --> 01:02:00,895
So this dagger was never...

780
01:02:01,336 --> 01:02:03,636
It cost 10 dollars
at a flea market.

781
01:02:04,466 --> 01:02:06,876
The fortune teller
only pops up...

782
01:02:06,876 --> 01:02:08,975
wherever it wants to
whenever it wants to.

783
01:02:09,305 --> 01:02:11,345
Darn rat.

784
01:02:11,345 --> 01:02:13,075
Right back at you.

785
01:02:13,216 --> 01:02:14,886
What was with the
silly Ji A act?

786
01:02:15,046 --> 01:02:16,185
Did you know it was me?

787
01:02:16,185 --> 01:02:19,586
I could smell the
metallic scent of blood.

788
01:02:20,086 --> 01:02:21,785
As you know, I have a
heightened sense of smell.

789
01:02:22,586 --> 01:02:24,796
Anyway, I thank you
for the donation.

790
01:02:26,825 --> 01:02:28,696
Knowing my secret...

791
01:02:28,696 --> 01:02:30,566
doesn't automatically
give you the upper hand.

792
01:02:30,995 --> 01:02:34,805
Even if you bury it elsewhere,
I'll still find a way back to her.

793
01:02:35,365 --> 01:02:38,336
I will keep doing so until
you hand over your body.

794
01:02:38,736 --> 01:02:42,705
So what you're saying is that I
can plant your soul elsewhere...

795
01:02:43,245 --> 01:02:44,305
by burying this.

796
01:02:46,776 --> 01:02:50,145
For instance... How
about that rat snake?

797
01:02:52,515 --> 01:02:53,656
I dare you to try.

798
01:02:57,955 --> 01:02:59,156
Don't tell me...

799
01:03:00,455 --> 01:03:02,426
you're expecting me...

800
01:03:02,566 --> 01:03:05,296
to be gently dragged
out of this body.

801
01:03:24,386 --> 01:03:26,856
Right. If I'm being honest,

802
01:03:26,856 --> 01:03:29,586
I like this piece of Imoogi
better than the other one.

803
01:03:29,986 --> 01:03:32,626
A villain should at
least be this crazy.

804
01:03:32,796 --> 01:03:34,926
Romance, my foot.

805
01:03:36,225 --> 01:03:39,895
This woman is and will
always be my hostage.

806
01:03:39,895 --> 01:03:42,236
The other piece of Imoogi is
more interested in Ji A...

807
01:03:42,236 --> 01:03:43,865
than being united with you.

808
01:03:44,066 --> 01:03:46,805
He is nothing but a
bunch of fragments.

809
01:03:46,805 --> 01:03:48,575
Not according to him though.

810
01:03:48,776 --> 01:03:51,946
You think you can pit
us against each other?

811
01:03:52,816 --> 01:03:53,915
Dream on.

812
01:03:56,685 --> 01:04:00,156
Do you even know what
he's up to right now?

813
01:04:02,555 --> 01:04:05,995
You see, he's...

814
01:04:23,406 --> 01:04:25,915
Irritating imbeciles.

815
01:04:51,516 --> 01:04:54,956
<font color="#00ff00">NAME: NAM JI A, DATE
OF BIRTH: MARCH 3, 1991</font>

816
01:04:54,956 --> 01:04:57,996
<font color="#00ff00">DATE OF DEATH:</font>

817
01:05:00,395 --> 01:05:02,465
<font color="#00ff00">DATE OF DEATH: TODAY</font>

818
01:05:17,225 --> 01:05:19,136
Innocent lives are
being sacrificed.

819
01:05:19,836 --> 01:05:22,705
It won't be long before
chaos sweeps the world.

820
01:05:22,765 --> 01:05:24,765
No, you're wrong.

821
01:05:25,975 --> 01:05:29,645
All along, you're the one
who's been chaos itself.

822
01:05:30,075 --> 01:05:32,145
- Honey.
- Don't call me that.

823
01:05:32,845 --> 01:05:34,145
For I...

824
01:05:35,285 --> 01:05:37,115
just decided to
give up that title.

825
01:05:37,386 --> 01:05:39,886
Don't be ridiculous.
On whose authority?

826
01:05:44,055 --> 01:05:45,196
Stop right there.

827
01:05:45,895 --> 01:05:47,126
You heard me!

828
01:05:47,325 --> 01:05:48,765
The moment you step
past those doors,

829
01:05:48,765 --> 01:05:50,196
you'll lose everything.

830
01:05:50,196 --> 01:05:51,736
I'll make sure of it!

831
01:06:24,825 --> 01:06:26,296
Are you okay?

832
01:06:41,785 --> 01:06:42,845
Yeon.

833
01:06:44,316 --> 01:06:46,256
Yes, it's me.

834
01:06:49,426 --> 01:06:50,486
Let's hurry.

835
01:06:51,156 --> 01:06:52,995
At least so I can be myself...

836
01:06:54,126 --> 01:06:56,026
right before it all ends.

837
01:07:00,095 --> 01:07:03,365
I want to be there beside you.

838
01:07:11,445 --> 01:07:12,575
Let's end this.

839
01:07:14,216 --> 01:07:15,985
Let's put an end...

840
01:07:17,586 --> 01:07:18,655
to this exhausting fight.

841
01:07:21,526 --> 01:07:24,826
<font color="#00ff00">THE LIST</font>

842
01:07:24,826 --> 01:07:26,295
<font color="#00ff00">NAME: NAM JI A, DATE
OF BIRTH: MARCH 3, 1991</font>

843
01:07:26,295 --> 01:07:27,736
<font color="#00ff00">DATE OF DEATH: TODAY</font>

844
01:07:27,736 --> 01:07:30,566
<font color="#00ff00">NAME: NAM JI A</font>

845
01:07:30,566 --> 01:07:37,476
<font color="#00ff00">DATE OF DEATH: TODAY</font>

846
01:08:00,588 --> 01:08:03,611
<b><font color="#00ff00">TALE OF THE NINE TAILED</font></b>

847
01:08:04,398 --> 01:08:05,596
<i>Just give me three more days.</i>

848
01:08:05,596 --> 01:08:08,044
<i>I can catch him! I
can catch Imoogi!</i>

849
01:08:08,274 --> 01:08:09,235
<i>It's too late.</i>

850
01:08:09,235 --> 01:08:10,535
<i>You'll regret this.</i>

851
01:08:10,947 --> 01:08:13,547
<i>If it weren't for me,
Yeon would still be...</i>

852
01:08:14,064 --> 01:08:17,604
<i>living as a mountain spirit.</i>

853
01:08:18,048 --> 01:08:19,758
<i>Yeon will never
forgive me for this.</i>

854
01:08:20,266 --> 01:08:22,535
<i>Don't make me regret
liking you, Yu Ri.</i>

855
01:08:22,535 --> 01:08:25,635
<i>I have the power to destroy
everything you care for.</i>

856
01:08:27,175 --> 01:08:30,045
<i>Let's join hands and kill the
gatekeeper of Samdo River.</i>

857
01:08:30,476 --> 01:08:31,545
<i>And what's the condition?</i>

858
01:08:31,906 --> 01:08:33,075
<i>Give me Ji A.</i>

